  "description": "Fix Featured Image Error Icon Positioning\n\nCorrect the positioning of the error icon that displays when the featured image fails to load in article components.\n\nRequirements:\n- Locate the image-error element within article-featured-image component\n- Add position: relative to the parent container (article-featured-image) to establish positioning context\n- Ensure the error icon displays in the intended location relative to the image container\n- Verify the error state displays correctly across different screen sizes and layouts\n- Test with both missing images and failed image loads to confirm proper positioning",
